title: el Kharafish
description: Nomadic desert campsite located near the Dakleh Oasis associated with the Sheikh Muftah culture. The site was seasonally occupied from about 3000-2200 BCE.

properties.description: Point representing the approximate location of the el Kharafish site, after Riemer 2008.
properties.title: Approximate imagery location of el Kharafish
